Invocation Name: make me rich quickly
des:
This Skill teaches you how to become rich quickly. A rich person is happy with what they have! Including their life setbacks.
Take your time in life but remember to learn everything only once, document what you learn and how you plan to apply it to your life. When you apply this principle you will look back six months later, and all of the things that you learned will be wonderfully incorporated into your life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
